name: Consistent Care Services- COVID Vaccine Site
vaccines: Janssen COVID-19 Vaccine, Pfizer-BioNTech COVID-19 Vaccine
info:
****All patients at this clinic will receive a $50 Visa gift card that can be used anywhere Visa is accepted.*** You will need to sign a consent form at the clinic verifying you received the gift card.  This is a clinic for 1st or 2nd doses of the Pfizer COVID-19 vaccine or the single dose of the Johnson & Johnson*** All patients 12 years old and older can register for the Pfizer vaccine only. (If 12-17 years old for the Pfizer vaccine, you must be with a parent or guardian or have parental/guardian consent) 
***Residents of ANY state are now eligible for the vaccine, but you still must have photo ID***
**Please do not come to your appointment if you are sick*** 

*VERY IMPORTANT*
***Please complete all the insurance/Medicare/Medicaid information when registering online for your appointment to avoid filling it out at the clinic***
special: If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
